				<li id="16555491" class="cmnt-root" data="58" data-d="1647944085000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578126/Hand-Ballista" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">22 Mar 2022 06:14</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16555491" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">As a Hint and a big up Note here , i Confirm you only need 20 Strength in order to Wield this Ballista. ( However you do need to 2 Hand it anyway , plus the only downside is that you cant Melee Hit attack with it on Horseback/Torrent ). Having just spending few extra Strength Point upto 15 STR , while Equipping Radagon&apos;s Soreseal which will make it upto 20 STR ahead. ( Then 2 Handing this Ballista is okay to Shoot Greatbolts with ). Ohh and another Cool Side note , Keep farming Big Bear Beasts there are 2 Farmable Bears in North Caelid by the Cliffside just before the Minor Erdtree from Dragonborrow. ( There&apos;s also a Mini-Boss shade called Hunter Bearing Boss that spawns at Night only which he can drop the Bell Bearing to have Inifinite Supplies of small thin Animl Bones and Hefty Animal Bones altho i suggest farming the Bears better as they are just 1 shot , Not Rune Bears just regular Bears in Dragonborrow Minor Erdtree ). There&apos;s also the Merchant ontop of Mt.Gelmir who sells infinite Explosive Bolts aswell.... Enjoy , as for the Jar Cannon you only need 25 or 26 Strength to 2 Hand it and Shoot with it altho the Ballista is fine. ( Golden Vow and Flame Grant Me Strength does also affect and increase the Damage further on with Regular Bolts from Golden Vow , and Flame Grant me Strength enhances the Explosive Bolts as they are considered Fire dmg-type ). Goodluck ;)</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16555491" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16555491" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>62</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>4</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16555491"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16555491" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16555491"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
				<li id="16555107" class="cmnt-root" data="4" data-d="1647943648000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578126/Hand-Ballista" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">22 Mar 2022 06:07</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16555107" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">This Ballista is actually really Handy in all situations specialy in Catacombs , Big Dungeons and entering Castles. ( Like Stormveil Castle , Raya Lucaria Academy , Lyndell Royal Academy , Volcano Manor , All Castle Areas and Sieges ). What you only need is a Bare-Minimum of 20 Strength and usually handling and shooting with this Ballista is that you have to 2 Hand it... So not neccessary 30 Strength.... Having this as a Back-up when your FP is finished like with my Build i&apos;m focusing mainly High INT with Dex ( My Strength is still 25 and i could use this Ballista while 2 handing it ). With Maximum upgrade this Ballista goes to 600 Physical Damage , but equipping Bone GreatBolts and Crafting them they deal actually +150 per shot. ( That means the Total Physical Damage Value is 750 not 600 as mentioned ). So respectfully this Ballista legit shoots 750 damage per shot , and while i have 80 INT my normal Glintstone Pebbles deals around that range with a Fully Upgraded Staff at +10... So this Ballista is not Bad specialy when facing tough large enemies , many small Enemies and busting your way thru while your FP is finished and no Potions at hand. ( Altho i do have my Blackbow at +10 , but with the Bow i generally use it for Status effects like Sleep , Poison , Bleed and Rot ). However in terms of damage the Ballista is insanely great specialy with a good Supply of Explosive Greatbolts your gonna literally wreck things up... You could farm up Runes , and then visit the Merchant uptop Mt.Gelmir he sells the Explosive Greatbolts where you can save them up for Boss Fight or clearing up Enemy Strongholds or Castles with this Ballista... ( And personally the Ballista feels much better than the Jar Cannon , with Reload Speed as the Jar Cannon loads much slower with just abit of damage increase which isn&apos;t that much by that point ). Goodluck.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16555107" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16555107" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>4</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16555107"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16555107" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16555107"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
